title: We Are Victors Not Victims | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: We Are Victors Not Victims | Victoria Osteen
description:
God calls us more than conquerors! We don't have to live captive to our thoughts—we can choose to think the thoughts of heaven.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
